``` mermaid

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Burger
    participant Wallet as EUDI Wallet
    participant QTSP as (Q)TSP / Issuer
    participant DIP as Discover Interface Provider
    participant AS as Authorization Server
    participant AuthN as Authentication Service
    participant ASIP as Authentic Source Interface Provider

    User->>QTSP: Verzoek om attestering/credential
    Note over User,QTSP: Burger wil credential in Wallet krijgen

    QTSP->>DIP: I1 Discover - search(attribute)
    DIP-->>QTSP: attributeIdentifier + metadata

    QTSP->>DIP: I1 Discover - retrieve(data service metadata)
    DIP-->>QTSP: endpointDescription + endpointURI + auth server metadata

    Note over QTSP,AS: Start Authorize-flow (OAuth 2.0 Authorization Code + PKCE)

    QTSP->>AS: Authorization Request\n(code_challenge, scope, redirect_uri, ...)
    AS->>AuthN: Start authenticatie/identificatie burger
    AuthN->>Wallet: Authorization Request\n(bijv. OpenID4VP request)
    Wallet->>User: Toon verzoek + vraag consent
    User-->>Wallet: Keurt goed + presenteert PID/eID
    Wallet-->>AuthN: Authorization Response\n(verifiable presentation met identificatiegegevens)
    AuthN-->>AS: Geauthenticeerde identiteit + resultaat
    AS-->>QTSP: Authorization Response\n(authorization code)

    QTSP->>AS: Token Request\n(code + code_verifier + client authentication)
    AS-->>QTSP: Access Token (JWT)\nmet identificatiegegevens van de burger

    alt Verificatiepad
        QTSP->>ASIP: I2 Verify + Access Token
        ASIP-->>QTSP: Verify Response
    else Ophalen van brondata
        QTSP->>ASIP: I3 Retrieve + Access Token
        ASIP-->>QTSP: Retrieve Response
    end

    QTSP->>Wallet: Issuance van credential\n(bijv. OpenID4VCI)
    Wallet-->>User: Credential opgeslagen

```
